    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "USAIR\nSystem Timetable\nEffective April 9, 1988\n28 New\nUSAir Cities\nthroughout\nthe West...\nbecause PSA is now USAir!\n© 1988 USAIR, INC.\nIncludes Allegheny Commuter Service",
      "SAN FRANCISCO\n1:00 P.M.\nPACIAC TIME\n2:00 P.M.\nMOUNTAIN TIME\nUSAIR\nService to over 100 cities in the U.S. and Canada.\nDENVER\nLOS ANGELES\nKANSAS CITY\n3:00 P.M.\nCENTRAL TIME\nMINNEAPOLIS/ST. PAUL\nMILWAUKEE\nID RAPIDETROIT\nCHICAGO\nST. LOUIS\nEVANSVI\nMEMPHIS\n4:00 P.M.\nEASTERN TIME\nMONTREAL\nBOSTON\nDICOTTI\nORK/NEWARK\nTON. D.C\n•GENIA BEACH\nUHAN\nPHOENIX\nTUCSON\nDALLAS/FT. WORTH\nAUSTIN\nSAN ANTONIO I\nTAMPAST… PETERSBURI\nFT. MYERS\nWEST PALM BEACH\nFORT LAUDERDALE\nINDIANAPOLIS I\nBUFFALO/NIAGARA FALLS\nJAMESTOWN\nFRANKLINIOL C\nAKRON/CANTON\nPITTSBURG\nLEXINGTO\nNASHVILLE\nITHACA\nBOSTON\n/BETHLEHEM/EASTON\nA/CAMDENN ILMINGTON\nMAYWILDWOOD\nGION, D.C\nUSAir \u0026\nAllegheny Commuter-\nA great team to go with.\nService to over 140 cities\nin the U.S. and Canada.\nALLEGHENY\nCOMMUTER\nService to over 60\ncities in the U.S.\nANDE\nVERO BEACH/FORT"
